                  <h2 className="text-5xl lg:text-9xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none">Yield<br/>Nodes.</h2>
                  <p className="serif italic text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/40 max-w-xl">
                    Managed liquidity pools synced with Cloud Firestore.
